Oh no! I won’t leave you “ she screamed back as the monstrous tendril of the unknown breast reached for her and she closed her eyes with tears streaming down her cheek. A young woman sighed while eating her Frosted Flakes and held her tender hand up to her cheek as she slowly chewed the cereal. She blinked and started to nod off before she heard the end credits roll. “Killer Squids from Planet Klorborp again?” she thought to herself while reading another bite of her cereal. Slowly she inserted the spoon into her mouth and the screen went to black. Channel 4 news anchor appeared in the right hand corner and gave a cheerful smile. “Rush INC plant has found a new home. Science Girls Vs The SpiderThe last ball rang out as another school day ended. As the students began filing out one-by-one, several of them were staying behind for the usual club activities and after-school projects. At least, that's what most of them were. One of them, seated in the school's computer room, was engaged in something less pressing. Science Club member Missy scowled at her computer screen. She didn't like how the situation was developing for her. She was down to her last healing item and the enemy still had six or seven troops left on their side. "I knew I should have taken more time to level-grind," she grumbled. It was only by chance that she felt the strand of webbing brush her hand. She glanced over at it and saw that it led upward. She looked up only for a split-second before it descended on her. *** Meanwhile, up on the fifth floor, the Science Club meeting was a few minutes away from getting started.
